title: Shope
about: A simple e-commerce website where you can buy products and add them to the cart. You can also filter products by category and search for products.

title: Nook
about: Reddit clone where you can post, comment, upvote, and downvote. You can also filter posts by category and search for posts.

title: Book Slayer
about: Book slayer is books libray where you can search for books and download them. You can also filter books by category and search for books.
